data.text: Mexico's Ruling Morena party claims to have won 12 of 15 gubernatorial votes. @mario_delgado only discounts Nuevo Leon, SLP and Queretaro, but claims Nayarit, Sinaloa, BCS, Chihuahua, Michoacan, Colima, Tlaxcala, Campeche, Guerrero, Zacatecas, BC, Sonora #Elecciones2021
